(4780, 'news', 248, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">Formation of the local management structures of &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC established on the basis of the Order dated April 11, 2016 of the president of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev has been completed. Procurement and supply bases and 55 base stations of the Company have been already established in 12 regions. The Company has started supply and procurement of food products in all regions of the country since January 01, 2017. On this occasion, the Company has begun two days training process with the participation of staff of the regional base. All the issues regarding all stages of the procurement process, acceptance of food products, their documentation, storage, sanitary and hygienic rules, transfer to procurement organizations, the importance of the modern logistics network, establishment of the product registration, packaging and marketing measures were stated in details, the opportunities of the company&rsquo;s portal were demonstrated, wide information was given about the instructions on use of the portal, its advantages for producers and buyers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">Speakers making speech at the event stated that the Joint Stock Company will play an important role in ensuring food security in the country. Establishment of the Joint Stock Company aims stimulating the production and processing of agricultural products, ensuring the development of the producers of the agricultural products, increasing the quality of food products, ensuring efficient use of public funds, improving the social welfare of the population engaged in the agriculture in the regions, ensuring fulfilment of procurement of the food products in the centralized order. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">At the same time, it was noted that all legal basis have been established for establishment of the necessary infrastructure and economical relations with the producers for successful implementation of the supply &ndash; procurement process since January 01 in the country. It was added that the partner farms have already been identified at the places in connection with the preparation for the procurement process and the necessary contracts have been concluded with them for purchasing products. Material and technical capacities of warehouses in the regions have been upgraded and sanitary and hygienic conditions have been fully ensured for the storage of food products.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">Based on the concept &quot;the system whose client is the state&quot;, besides the procurement services in the regions, the Joint Stock company intends to provide the local producers with comprehensive support regarding provision of consulting services and modern innovations. To this end, educating meetings will be held with farmers in the regions and their integration into new scientific knowledge will be ensured.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">At the end of the two-day training, new service cars were presented to the regional supply &ndash; procurement bases.<img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/FA7A6452.JPG\" style=\"width: 5760px; height: 3840px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/FA7A6474.JPG\" style=\"width: 5760px; height: 3840px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(4781, 'news', 248, 'en', 'short', 'Formation of the local management structures of “Food Products’ Procurement and Supply” OJSC established on the basis of the Order dated April 11, 2016 of the president of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev has been completed. Procurement and supply bases and 55 base stations of the Company have been already established in 12 regions. The Company has started supply and procurement of food products in all regions of the country since January 01, 2017. On this occasion, the Company has begun two days training process with the participation of staff of the regional base. All the issues regarding all stages of the procurement process, acceptance of food products, their documentation, storage, sanitary and hygienic rules, transfer to procurement organizations, the importance of the modern logistics network, establishment of the product registration, packaging and marketing measures were stated in details, the opportunities of the company’s portal were demonstrated, wide information was given about the instructions on use of the portal, its advantages for producers and buyers.'),
