(4839, 'news', 252, 'en', 'title', 'LOCAL PRODUCTS WILL BE PROCURED'),
(4840, 'news', 252, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Next meeting was held with the participation of the heads of the structural divisions and regional offices in the central building of &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC. Opening the meeting, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors Khalig Mammadov stated that the supply system of the procurement organizations financed by the state budget has begun functioning successfully in line with the tasks set by the President of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Joint Stock Company will start the product procurement process from the agricultural producers sooner. To this end, designing the procurement plans for the regions will be completed in the near future. The regional divisions were given tasks to reveal the agrarian potential of the regions, to gather information on the current state of the local production, to identify the procurement volume of the staff of the regional division of the company by calculating per each village and regions and to specify the proposals of the manufacturers. It was stated that the control on quality and packaging of the products to be procured from the countrymen would be strengthened. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Deputy Chairman of the Board Elshan Asadov spoke in the meeting and gave recommendations on warehouse management in the regions, formation of adroit staff potential for successful implementation of the procurement process, increasing the knowledge and skills of employees, increasing control on the documentation in the process of procurement and supply of products.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Then, they exchanged views on the organizational issues and gave assignments to the department managers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/IMG_0514.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/IMG_0515.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(4841, 'news', 252, 'en', 'short', 'Next meeting was held with the participation of the heads of the structural divisions and regional offices in the central building of \"Food Products’ Procurement and Supply\" OJSC. Opening the meeting, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors Khalig Mammadov stated that the supply system of the procurement organizations financed by the state budget has begun functioning successfully in line with the tasks set by the President of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev. '),
