(4870, 'news', 254, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A meeting was held with young employees at &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC. The Chairman of the Board of Directors Abulfat Gojayev congratulated the employees in connection with the Youth day. The Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors Elshan Asadov spoke about the history of February 2 Youth Day and emphasized the special role of the national leader Heydar Aliyev in establishment of this day. He noted that the state&#39;s attention and care towards young people is at high level. In his opinion, today the young people of Azerbaijan demonstrate activity outside the country and represent our country worthily. &quot;Every young person shall be distinguished by his / her potential and intellectual qualities at the work place and try to justify the confidence given to them&quot; said Asadov and emphasized that, as in the most institutions, the young people prevail in the structures of the Joint Stock Company and the management always try to approach them carefully.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Finally, congratulations were expressed regarding the holiday and the necessary recommendations were given.</span></span></p>'),
(4871, 'news', 254, 'en', 'short', 'A meeting was held with young employees at \"Food Products’ Procurement and Supply\" OJSC. The Chairman of the Board of Directors Abulfat Gojayev congratulated the employees in connection with the Youth day. The Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors Elshan Asadov spoke about the history of February 2 Youth Day and emphasized the special role of the national leader Heydar Aliyev in establishment of this day. He noted that the state&#39;s attention and care towards young people is at high level. In his opinion, today the young people of Azerbaijan demonstrate activity outside the country and represent our country worthily. \"Every young person shall be distinguished by his / her potential and intellectual qualities at the work place and try to justify the confidence given to them\" said Asadov and emphasized that, as in the most institutions, the young people prevail in the structures of the Joint Stock Company and the management always try to approach them carefully.'),
