(4899, 'news', 256, 'en', 'title', 'A REGIONAL MEETING WAS HELD IN YEVLAKH'),
(4900, 'news', 256, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC holds educating meetings with the manufacturers and representatives of the procurement organizations functioning in the regions in order to fulfill the tasks set by the Head of State at the conference dedicated to the third year of implementation of the State Program on &ldquo;Social - economic development of the regions of Azerbaijan Republic in 2014-2018&rdquo;. Immediately after the President&#39;s assignments, the Joint Stock Company held business meetings with the representatives of more than 400 public procurement organizations operating in Aran regions - in Salyan and Kurdamir and the organizations operating in Absheron region - in Sumgayit. Today, the next regional educating meetings have been held in Yevlakh, Aghdash, Ujar, Goychay and Mingachevir.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">200 people, including heads of the structural divisions of the Joint Stock Company, procurement organizations and local executive bodies participated in the meeting held in Yevlakh. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Making speech in the meeting, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC Khalig Mammadov stated that the purpose of these meetings was listening to the proposals in order to reveal the production &ndash; procurement potential in the regions, to direct the products produced in the regions to the food demand of the public procurement organizations, as well as to increase the supply level. The speaker said that if the food demand of the educational institutions, nurseries and kindergartens, hospitals and military units in each region is met on the account of the production capacities of the region, large volume of funds will enter the regions and local production will be stimulated. The main objective is supporting budget savings, ensuring transparency and supporting small and medium-sized businesses.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Making speech in the regional meeting, the Head of &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC Abbas Hajiyev spoke in details about the preparations for the procurement process. The Joint Stock Company is ready to purchase products from farmers regardless their size against average market prices anywhere in the country. Manufacturers of the products shall appeal to the company and be registered in the electron portal and post their proposal.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Later, numerous questions were answered by the representatives of the state procurement organizations, proposals on increase of the procurement and supply level were registered, the heads of the structural divisions were instructed for execution of some of these proposals. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The persons making speech in the meeting highly estimated the activities of the Company established by the head of the state and noted that provision of the educational institutions by foods had been increased thanks to the supply level begun from January. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC will continue to hold educating regional meetings with the procurement organizations.</span></span></p>'),
(4901, 'news', 256, 'en', 'short', '\"Food Products’ Procurement and Supply\" OJSC holds educating meetings with the manufacturers and representatives of the procurement organizations functioning in the regions in order to fulfill the tasks set by the Head of State at the conference dedicated to the third year of implementation of the State Program on “Social - economic development of the regions of Azerbaijan Republic in 2014-2018”. Immediately after the President&#39;s assignments, the Joint Stock Company held business meetings with the representatives of more than 400 public procurement organizations operating in Aran regions - in Salyan and Kurdamir and the organizations operating in Absheron region - in Sumgayit. Today, the next regional educating meetings have been held in Yevlakh, Aghdash, Ujar, Goychay and Mingachevir.'),
