(4914, 'news', 257, 'en', 'title', 'PROCUREMENT AND SUPPLY LEVEL WAS DISCUSSED'),
(4915, 'news', 257, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">The Joint Stock Company has started the supply of procurement organizations (educational institutions, nurseries, kindergartens, hospitals, military units, other state facilities and so on) starting from January 1, 2017.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">A regional meeting was held in Gabala city upon Sheki - Gabala Regional division (Sheki, Gabala, Oguz) with the participation of public procurement organizations and representatives of the executive bodies. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">Making speech in the meeting, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC Khalig Mammadov spoke about the development of the non-oil sector under the leadership of the head of the state in the recent years. He stated that, foundation of the Company by the President of Azerbaijan Republic would contribute to the formation of the supply chain in the agrarian sector, procurement of the products manufactured by farmers, as well as increase of the procurement level of the procurement organizations. The Company holds regional meetings, surveys and monitoring for increasing the procurement and supply level in line with the instructions of the head of the state. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">He stated that the purpose of these meetings was listening to the proposals in order to reveal the production &ndash; procurement potential in the regions, to direct the products produced in the regions to the food demand of the public procurement organizations, as well as to increase the supply level. The speaker said that if the food demand of the educational institutions, nurseries and kindergartens, hospitals and military units in each region is met on the account of the production capacities of the region, large volume of funds will enter the regions and local production will be stimulated. The main objective is supporting budget savings, ensuring transparency and supporting small and medium-sized businesses.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">The demand on the food stuff of the procurement organizations, rules of use of the electron portal (</span><a href=\"http://www.tedaruk.az\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">www.tedaruk.az</span></a><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">), the instructions on the registration procedures were explained in the regional meeting. It was recommended to each procurement organization to post its demand correctly on the portal and the demands should be in line with real needs for proper use of the public funds. In this direction, many questions of the directors of kindergartens, representatives of hospitals were responded and their ability to work with the portal as explained in details. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">At the end of the regional meeting, the representatives of the procurement organizations expressed their proposals for increasing the level of procurement and supply.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">&ldquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC will continue to hold the educating regional meetings with the procurement organizations in the regions. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/14.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
