(5020, 'news', 264, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC has been trying to protect the economic interest of the farmers since its establishment and therefore, the agricultural products are procured from the farmers by the local structures of the company and offered to the consumers in the fairs organized in the capital every week. The company has strengthened the procurement process in connection with Novruz holiday and the volume of the products procured from the regional farmers and transported to the capital has been increased. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC has started the sale of the agricultural products procured from the local farmers in the regions in connection with the beginning of Novruz holiday. Today, the agricultural products procured from some regions of the country have been put in the fairs organized in several places of the capital. The products transported by the vehicles of the company are purchased at the average market prices from the farmers. The addresses of the fairs: </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Binagadi region:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- Darnagul dwelling area, yard of vocational lyceum № 6;;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Khatai region</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- near Baku Cinema;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Sumgayit city</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The territory of old bus station. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Nearly 100 tons agricultural products have been proposed to the organized fairs by the Company. Consumers are offered the same amount and variety of products on holidays.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC will organize its activities incessantly and will try to provide the residents of the capital with cheap and high quality agricultural products during holidays.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/22.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 1000px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(5021, 'news', 264, 'en', 'short', '“Food Products’ Procurement and Supply” OJSC has been trying to protect the economic interest of the farmers since its establishment and therefore, the agricultural products are procured from the farmers by the local structures of the company and offered to the consumers in the fairs organized in the capital every week. The company has strengthened the procurement process in connection with Novruz holiday and the volume of the products procured from the regional farmers and transported to the capital has been increased. '),
