(5049, 'news', 266, 'en', 'title', 'HOLIDAY PRESENTS WERE OFFERED TO FRONT LINE COUNTRYMEN'),
(5050, 'news', 266, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC met with the inhabitants of the villages located in the frontline of Gazakh region in connection with Novruz holiday. Detailed information about the activities of the Company was given to the inhabitants of Gushchu Ayrim, Bala Jafarli and Mazam villages in the meeting held with the support of Gazakh region Executive Power. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Gasim Shiriyev, head of the Department of Export and Domestic Market Investments, organization of export of &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC stated that the company had been established by Order 1944 dated April 11, 2016 of the President of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev. The main purpose of Joint Stock Company is stimulating the production and processing of agricultural products, ensuring the development of the producers of the agricultural products, increasing the quality of food products, ensuring efficient use of public funds, improving the social welfare of the population engaged in the agriculture in the regions, ensuring fulfilment of procurement of the food products in the centralized order. The organization will support social - economic development of the villages located in the border and front lines and procure all kind of products produced here in accordance with the instructions of the President of the country. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">To this end, the regional structures of the organization have been instructed to calculate the production capacities of the border and frontline villages and to purchase all types of products of the rural population at the market price and to sell them in the domestic and foreign markets. It was noted that the residents of the villages in the border and front line will be given advance payment for sowing purposes in accordance with the priorities of the Joint Stock Company,</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Congratulating the countrymen on the occasion of holiday, the employees of the Company emphasized that Mountainous Garabagh conflict will be settled very soon under the leadership of the president of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev and all our compatriots who were driven out from their homes will return back to their homeland. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At the end of the meeting &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC offered holiday presents to 500 inhabitants (1600 people) of Gushchu Ayrim, Ala Jafarli and Mazam villages.</span></span></p>'),
(5051, 'news', 266, 'en', 'short', '“Food Products’ Procurement and Supply” OJSC met with the inhabitants of the villages located in the frontline of Gazakh region in connection with Novruz holiday. Detailed information about the activities of the Company was given to the inhabitants of Gushchu Ayrim, Bala Jafarli and Mazam villages in the meeting held with the support of Gazakh region Executive Power. '),
