(5064, 'news', 267, 'en', 'title', 'CONTROL MEASURES HAVE BEEN STRENGTHENED'),
(5065, 'news', 267, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The Company&#39;s management are regularly on business trips in the regions of the country and the problems encountered during the procurement and supply process are promptly investigated and settled for local monitoring of the realized works. A five-day business trip was made to all regions within 01.01.2017 - 05.01.2017, problems arisen in organizing and supplying process were resolved on-site. 12 educating regional meetings were held with the representatives of the public procurement organizations from 01.02.2017 to 10.03.2017 encircling all regions and more than 2117 representatives of the procurement organizations were informed about the operations of the Company, the portal (<a href=\"http://www.tedaruk.az\">www.tedaruk.az</a>) of demand on food products of the procurement organizations in these meetings and consequently, they have achieved to increase the supply level. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The management of the Joint Stock Company was on business trip in the regions of the republic during Novruz holiday and learned the current condition of the procurement and supply level. A delegation consisting of the Chairman of the Board of Directors Abulfat Gojayev, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors Elshan Asadov, Head of the Department of organization of Procurement and Supply Abbas Hajiyev, Head of the Monitoring and Commodity Turnover Coordination Department Sahib Shukurov made acquaintance with the work of the structures operating in the regions and learned the state of organizing, the professionalism of the personnel, supply of the procurement organizations with food products, the current state of the warehouse infrastructure and decisions were made for achieving prompt management. Meetings were held with each regional division and the staffs of the base stations in the regions and the proposals were listened to for increasing the service level. Relevant tasks were given to increase the supply of public procurement organizations with foodstuffs and new tasks were identified.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Another goal of the visits of the company&rsquo;s management to the regions was holding mutual meetings with the manufactures of the agricultural products. Therefore, several meetings were held with the local manufactures having concluded cooperation contracts with the Company. Sowing areas of the manufactures were observed, their production potential was studied, future perspectives of cooperation were reviewed. The regional manufactures were informed that the organization is ready to procure the products of each manufacturer at the field in line with the relevant instructions of the head of the state. Product of each farmer producing qualitative product will be procured at the average market price. The sowing areas, farming habits of the manufacturers were reviewed and regional structures were instructed regarding procurement of the agricultural products during the visit of the collaborators of the company. It was emphasized during the meeting with the farmers that procurement points and procurement agents will be indentified upon the villages for ensuring high level of the procurement system encircling all regions. Special attention will be paid to the economic potential, specialization traditions in the agricultural sector of each region during the procurement process. Positions for holding educating meetings with the local manufactures were identified by the relevant structures of the company.</span></span></p>'),
(5066, 'news', 267, 'en', 'short', 'The Company&#39;s management are regularly on business trips in the regions of the country and the problems encountered during the procurement and supply process are promptly investigated and settled for local monitoring of the realized works. A five-day business trip was made to all regions within 01.01.2017 - 05.01.2017, problems arisen in organizing and supplying process were resolved on-site. 12 educating regional meetings were held with the representatives of the public procurement organizations from 01.02.2017 to 10.03.2017 encircling all regions and more than 2117 representatives of the procurement organizations were informed about the operations of the Company, the portal (www.tedaruk.az) of demand on food products of the procurement organizations in these meetings and consequently, they have achieved to increase the supply level. '),
