(5110, 'news', 270, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A Memorandum of Understanding has been concluded between &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot;&nbsp;OJSC and &ldquo;IDROMECCANICA LUCCHINI SpA&rdquo; company on the construction of modern greenhouses for vegetable production in Azerbaijan.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The press service of the OJSC informed AZERTAJ that the Memorandum was signed by the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Company Abulfat Gojayev abd the sales manager of the Italian company Cesare Ghizzi. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">According to the signed Memorandum, the Italian company will carry out the construction, co-management of greenhouses in Azerbaijan, the formation of workforce potential and provision of the employees with necessary technical knowledge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The Italian party will establish the company &ldquo;Lucchini-Az&rdquo; and a joint venture will be established between &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC and &ldquo;Lucchini-Az&rdquo; for realization of the project.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Joint Stock Company undertook all necessary work for the implementation of the project &ndash;water, electricity and settlement of all issues suitable for the road.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Costs and arrangements for establishment of an infrastructure will be considered after signing the contract. It is planned to invest 13 million euro in the construction of greenhouses at the initial stage.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Following the signing ceremony, the management of the OJSC and the representatives of the Italian company conducted reviews on the areas where the greenhouses were to be built and held consultations. The area located in Zire settlement of the Caspian region was estimated as a successful choice for the construction of a greenhouse complex by foreign guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">It was noted that &ldquo;IDROMECCANICA LUCCHINI SpA&rdquo; company of Italy carries out construction of the greenhouse complexes growing agricultural products based on the innovative technologies in many countries. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/90.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(5111, 'news', 270, 'en', 'short', 'A Memorandum of Understanding has been concluded between «Food Products’ Procurement and Supply» OJSC and “IDROMECCANICA LUCCHINI SpA” company on the construction of modern greenhouses for vegetable production in Azerbaijan.'),
