(5125, 'news', 271, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A training in the subject &ldquo;Rules of use of the portal by the procurement organizations&rdquo; was held in the central building of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC for the employees working as operators in the regional divisions of the company. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The director of the Information and Electron services sector of the Joint Stock Company Vusal Asgarov gave information about the purpose of the training. He said that the Joint Stock Company will conduct educating trainings for increasing professionalism of the employees on the initiative of the management of the company. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The specialist of the Information and electron services sector Kamran Valiyev made a presentation and demonstrated registration procedure of the procurement organizations on the food stuff demand portal (www.tedaruk.az).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The accountant of the accounting sector Iman Najafov gave information on entrance of the demand of 2017 into the portal through correct procedures. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Then the questions of the employees were answered and on-site trainings were conducted with the operators for assimilation of the given tasks. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Educating trainings will be continued for increasing professionalism of the employees. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/18-2222.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></p>'),
(5126, 'news', 271, 'en', 'short', 'A training in the subject “Rules of use of the portal by the procurement organizations” was held in the central building of «Food Products’ Procurement and Supply» OJSC for the employees working as operators in the regional divisions of the company. '),
