(5139, 'news', 272, 'en', 'title', '“SOUTH KOREAN COMPANIES ARE INTERESTED IN COOPERATION WITH YOUR COMPANY”'),
(5140, 'news', 272, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A meeting was held with the Ambassador of South Korea Republic to Azerbaijan Mr. Kim Chiang Gyu at the headquarters of &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC. Increasing the intergovernmental import-export relations, importance of the commercial turnover, possibility of exportation of the Azerbaijani products to South Korea was discussed in the meeting held on the basis of the invitation of the Chairman of the Board of Directors Abulfat Gojayev. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Abulfat Gojayev stated that the organization is interested in studying South Korean experience in accordance with its &quot;Strategic Development Plan&quot;. To this end, mutual visits and joint participation at the exhibitions and fairs can be organized in logistics, management of commodity circulation on the basis of modern technologies, personnel training and other areas. Using the South Korean technologies in the field of processing of the agricultural products, the possibility of bringing machinery and mechanisms to Azerbaijan with special concessions and the expansion of mutual cooperation in this direction are of great importance for the Company. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The Ambassador Kim Jong-gyu welcomed the proposals with interest and stated that the agrarian reforms recently conducted under the President of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev, provision of the agricultural areas by modern technologies are watched with interest in their country. Establishment of &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC by the President of Azerbaijan Republic is an important event. My country has rich experience in establishment of the procurement and supply system in the agrarian sector. The South Korean companies are interested in the cooperation with your company.&nbsp; At present, there are favourable opportunities for exporting modern technologies to Azerbaijan and ecologically clean products to South Korea. Such products as pomegranate, date, grape, hazelnut, walnut and many other products of Azerbaijan may be exported to South Korea. I will do all my best in this field as a diplomat&rdquo; &ndash; the ambassador said. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The quality standards, packaging and logistics required for the exportation of goods of Azerbaijan were widely discussed during the mutual discussions. It was decided to conduct next business meeting with the Korean International Cooperation Agency (Koica) and the Trade Department of the Embassy of Korea Republic in the near future. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At the end of the meeting, Chairman of the Board of Directors of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC Abulfat Gojayev presented Garabagh carpet to the Korean diplomat.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/IMG_0706.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/1mc.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(5141, 'news', 272, 'en', 'short', 'A meeting was held with the Ambassador of South Korea Republic to Azerbaijan Mr. Kim Chiang Gyu at the headquarters of “Food Products’ Procurement and Supply” OJSC. Increasing the intergovernmental import-export relations, importance of the commercial turnover, possibility of exportation of the Azerbaijani products to South Korea was discussed in the meeting held on the basis of the invitation of the Chairman of the Board of Directors Abulfat Gojayev. '),
