(5214, 'news', 277, 'en', 'title', 'JOINT STOCK COMPANY SIGNED A MEMORANDUM WITH “YTO GROUP”'),
(5215, 'news', 277, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC plans to manufacture medium sized tractors for small family farms in Azerbaijan together with &ldquo;YTO GROUP&rdquo;. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Today, it has been widely discussed with the representatives of the cooperation at the central office of Joint Stock Company and a memorandum of cooperation has been signed. The Memorandum has been signed by the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Abulfat Gojayev and the representative of &ldquo;YTO GROUP&rdquo; in Azerbaijan Farhad Mammadov. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The Vice President of YTO GROUP Shan Chunyu expressed his satisfaction on the cooperation and spoke about the work to be done.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">According to the Memorandum, averagely 800 medium-sized (18-40 horsepower) YTO tractors will be assembled per a year at the production facility in Gusar region. It was decided to allocate loans for exportation of the spare parts of tractors as the result of negotiations held with the Chinese company. Other spare parts except tractor engines and transmission facilities will be purchased from various enterprises operating in Azerbaijan from the second year and it will exert positive impact on the development of additional various industries. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">YTO tractors that will be jointly manufactured will be sold to our local farmers under favourable conditions through &ldquo;Agrolizing&rdquo; OJSC. After payment of 20% of the value, the rest amount will be divided into equal instalments for 10 years (120 months), thus, farmers will be able to buy a tractor by paying small amount. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Simplicity of the technical specifications of YTO tractors, ease of use will allow farmers to use the technique without any additional vocational training. Compared with alternative brands, these tractors are distinguished by low cost, availability of high pressure fuel pump, power, spare parts quality and reasonable price, low fuel consumption. YTO tractors are widely used in gardening, vegetable growing, tobacco cultivation, feed growing and greenhouse industries. According to the researches, there is great need for small-sized tractors in the farms of our country. In particular, these techniques will play an important role in reducing labour costs in small households, ensuring the production process intensity and reducing losses. Tractor carries out inter-row technical works, cultivation measures, field harvesting and other important work in a short term allowing to work in small sowing areas. Establishment of production of YTO tractors in Azerbaijan will contribute to rapid renovation of the agricultural machinery and technique park.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">According to the signed memorandum, &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC will provide farmers with active support in the opening of training centers for habits of utilization of the techniques, sales organization, technical support and other issues.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/16.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
