(5244, 'news', 279, 'en', 'title', 'JOINT STOCK COMPANY CONDUCTED EDUCATING DISCUSSION FOR FARMERS'),
(5245, 'news', 279, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A business meeting of producers and companies dealing with agricultural production was held today in Baku Expo Center organized by &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC within the 11th Azerbaijan International Agricultural Exhibition &ldquo;CASPIAN AQRO-2017&rdquo;. The foreign partners of the Joint Stock Company - &quot;Eurochem&quot; from Russia and &ldquo;YTO GROUP&rdquo; state corporation of China also attended the meeting.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Opening the meeting, Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Khalig Mammadov said that agrarian reforms carried out under the leadership of the President Ilham Aliyev have led to serious agricultural development in recent years. Returning to land has started all over the country. However, it is extremely important to increase the fertility indicators in establishment of the civilized farming principles. To this end, farmers shall use modern technologies and fertilizers that increase soil fertility and increase productivity within the standards. Mineral fertilizers easily dissolved in water and having organic character are widely used in the world. &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC cooperates with the leading foreign companies in the field of fertilizer production and tries to apply these fertilizers in the sowing areas of our country.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Speaking at the conference, the representative of &ldquo;Eurochem&rdquo; company of Russia Vladislav Udovchenko made a presentation on specifications of mineral fertilizers and their positive impacts on the plant vegetation. He said that mineral fertilizers playing a direct role in raising the productivity of the plant are the most important tool in achieving sustainable productivity today. Farmers use some types of fertilizers in Azerbaijan, their number can be increased and thus expansion of intensive sowing can be ensured. Other representatives of &ldquo;Eurochem&rdquo; company made presentations for our local farmers attended the meeting and demonstrated them the specifications of the water soluble mineral fertilizers having no adverse effect on ecology. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The representatives of companies operating in the field of technical support, consulting, spoke at the conference and said that they highly appreciated the agrarian reforms in Azerbaijan and expressed their interest in cooperation.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Summing up the conference, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC Elshan Asadov spoke about the advance payments made to the farmers on the basis of the instruction of the head of the state and consulting services in the agrarian sector. He stated that the Joint Stock Company plans to bring the mineral fertilizers used in the world practice to the country and to sell them to local farmers at the discounted rate. This step will seriously contribute to the development of households and will cause to increase of the production in small farms and to higher quality indicators. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A lot of questions of the farmers were answered in the discussion.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC will continue to conduct educating meetings for farmers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/19-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/19-1.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/19-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
