(5259, 'news', 280, 'en', 'title', 'CONFERENCE DEDICATED TO THE 99TH ANNIVERSARY OF AZERBAIJAN PEOPLE\'S REPUBLIC'),
(5260, 'news', 280, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Today, a conference dedicated to the 99<sup>th</sup> anniversary of Azerbaijan People&rsquo;s Republic was organized by &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot;&nbsp;OJSC. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At first, the national anthem was played and a video film about the establishment of the People&#39;s Republic was watched.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Opening the event, the Deputy Chairman of the Joint Stock Company Khalig Mammadov spoke about the tense geopolitical events taken place at the beginning of XX century and development of the first democratic republic established in the East. He stated that the national-minded sons of Azerbaijan had declared the Azerbaijan Democratic Republic on May 28, 1918. It was a parliamentary state as the first democratic republic in the East. Its state attributes - flag, anthem and emblems were accepted. Its three-color flag reflected Turkism, Islamism and modernism.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Realizing their national struggle at the end of the XX century, our people united around our national Leader Heydar Aliyev and restored the independent statehood values and turned Azerbaijan into a powerful and modern state. At present, strengthening of our independent statehood and integration into the international world is carried out decently by the President Ilham Aliyev. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Professor of Baku State University Anar Isgandarov made speech at the conference and spoke about tense political processes of the XX century: &ldquo;Establishment of Azerbaijan People&rsquo;s Republic is an important historical event. Mass genocide was committed against our people at that time, Azerbaijanis were completely removed from Baku. Stepan Shaumyan killed brutally the people in all regions of the country with its 20 thousand dashnak army. Under this tense political condition, the members of Muslim Fraction, that is to say that of Transcaucasia Muslim Council conducted a separate meeting and decided to declare the independence of Azerbaijan. To this end, Transcaucasia Muslim Council declared itself as the National Council of Azerbaijan, exactly, Azerbaijan Parliament. Thus, in fact, the first parliament was established in the history of Azerbaijan and the first parliamentary republic was founded. De-facto recognition of the independent of Azerbaijan Republic at Paris Peace Conference conducted on January 11, 1920 was one of the unprecedented victories&rdquo;.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The conference was continued as a debate with the questions asked from the historian scientist.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/26-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/26-1.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(5261, 'news', 280, 'en', 'short', 'Today, a conference dedicated to the 99th anniversary of Azerbaijan People’s Republic was organized by «Food Products’ Procurement and Supply» OJSC. '),
