(5289, 'news', 282, 'en', 'title', 'NATIONAL SALVATION DAY WAS CELEBRATED'),
(5290, 'news', 282, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">June 15 &ndash; National Salvation day was celebrated at &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At first, the participants of the conference watched a video film about the essence of the events of June, 1993. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Making speech at the conference, the member of the National Assembly, chairman of Garadagh district organization Aydin Huseynov stated that ungovernable actions carried out by some armed groups functioning in the republic at the beginning of 1993, fraternal slaughter inside Azerbaijan and serving as a background for the civil war, inclination to separatism and disintegration in different regions provoked the plan of putting an end to the existence of Azerbaijan as a state. Notwithstanding two years independence history, the state couldn&rsquo;t get rid of the volte face waves. The disobedience of the military unit under the leadership of the Collonel Suret Huseynov against the government in Ganja on October 4, 1993 led the country to chaos. The urgent steps taken by the government for controlling the situation couldn&rsquo;t improve the situation. Under this condition, both the political power and the people sought assistance from Nakhchivan &ndash; Heydar Aliyev having rich political experience. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Basing on the national interest, our Great Leader came to Baku and eliminated political and military tension in a short term.&rdquo; Emphasizing these ideas, the editor &ndash; in &ndash; chief of the newspaper &ldquo;Iki Sahil&rdquo;, member of YAP Political Council Vugar Rahimzade also spoke about the political activities of the National Leader Heydar Aliyev during the tense political situation of the country. He stated that the National Leader came back to power by the demand of the people and put an end to the political crisis and stability period began in Azerbaijan. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Summing up the conference, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC Elshan Asadov estimated the events of June 15 as the beginning of a new page in our modern history. &ldquo;The constitution was adopted and statehood institutions were formed, economic reforms were carried out. Hydrocarbon reserves of Azerbaijan were opened to the world. Today, our country moves confidentially towards the strategic direction defined by our National Leader. Our army becomes stronger, works carried out on the areas liberated from the occupation, especially in Jojug Marjanli village encourage our people. The visit of the President Ilham Aliyev to Jojug Marjanli village and reviewing the renovation and construction works is the bright military victory of economically strengthening Azerbaijan&rdquo;.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/15-2.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/15-1.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/15-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
