(5320, 'news', 284, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/21-5.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/21-6.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/21-7.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC continues the educating events among the manufactures of the agricultural products. The next scientific seminar was organized by the Joint Stock Company for the agronomists working in the greenhouses. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The representatives of the foreign partners of the Joint Stock Company - &ldquo;Eurochem&rdquo; from Russia and other companies attended the meeting. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Opening the meeting, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Elshan Asadov stated that the agrarian reforms under the leadership of the President Ilham Aliyev had led to serious development of agriculture in the recent years. Utilization of fertilizers plays an important role in the establishment of the civilized sowing principles and improving the productivity. Farmers shall use modern technologies and apply the mineral fertilizers increasing fertility of soil and improving productivity within the standards. Mineral fertilizers easily dissolved in water and having organic character are widely used in the world. &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC cooperates with the leading foreign companies in the field of fertilizer production and tries to apply these fertilizers in the sowing areas of our country.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Making presentation for the agronomists the Director in Turkey of the Spanish company &ldquo;Agroquimica Codiagro&rdquo; Mehmet Chiloghlu gave information about the role of fertilizers in the development of plants. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The sales director of &ldquo;Eurochem&rdquo; Firdausa Yunusova spoke about the technical parameters of water-soluble mineral fertilizers and the positive effects on the plant vegetation. He stated that the mineral fertilizers playing direct role in raising the productivity of the plant are one of the most important tools for obtaining sustainable products today. Farmers in Azerbaijan use a number of fertilizers, their number may be increased by expanding intensive crops. The microelements complex in these fertilizers is fully absorbed by the leaves of plants, it strengthens their root system and improves the foreign appearance of the plant. The agronomists growing plants in the greenhouses shall be interested in these fertilizers. Other economic importance of water soluble fertilizers is not requiring additional agro-technical care. These fertilizers are solved in water and applied in the plant through the pivot system in the open and closed areas and there is no need for technical care during while sowing dry fertilizers. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Another important economic significance of fertilizers in the water is that they do not require additional costs during agro care. These fertilizers are mixed with water in the open and closed areas by means of the pivot system to the plant, which ultimately does not require the required techniques for drying of dry fertilizers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Speaking in the meeting, other specialists made different presentations for local agronomists and demonstrated the technical indicators of the water soluble mineral fertilizers and other herbal medicines not exerting negative impact on the ecology. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Scientific data, innovations were highly appreciated by the agronomists, discussions were made on the subject and numerous questions were answered. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC will continue to conduct educating meetings. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At the end, iftar table was laid for the participants of the seminar.</span></span></p>'),
