(5349, 'news', 286, 'en', 'title', '“AZTT-LUCCHINI” LLC WAS FOUNDED'),
(5350, 'news', 286, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A draft decision on establishment of &ldquo;AZTT-LUCCHINI&rdquo; and its Charter was signed with the Italian Company &ldquo;LUCCHINI.AZ&rdquo; at the central office of &rdquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC. The documents were signed by the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Abulfat Gojayev and the representative of &ldquo;LUCCHINI.AZ&rdquo; LLC Massimo Lucchini. The shareholding in the authorized capital of &ldquo;AZTT-LUCCHINI&rdquo; LLC founded under the Civil Code of Azerbaijan Republic and other legislative acts is defined as following: </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&bull; &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC - 51%</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&bull; &quot;LUCCHINI.AZ&quot; - 49%</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&ldquo;AZTT-LUCCHINI&rdquo; LLC will carry out construction of greenhouses, joint management, formation of the working staff, provision of the employees with necessary scientific and technical knowledge. A memorandum of understanding was signed between &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC and the Italian Company &ldquo;IDROMECCANICA LUCCHINI SpA&rdquo; in April. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Joint Stock Company undertook all necessary work for the implementation of the project &ndash;water, electricity and settlement of all issues suitable for the road. Costs and arrangements for establishment of an infrastructure will be considered after signing the contract. It is planned to invest 13 million euro in the construction of greenhouses at the initial stage.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Following the signing ceremony, the management of the OJSC and the representatives of the Italian company conducted reviews on the areas where the greenhouses were to be built and held consultations. The area located in Zire settlement of the Caspian region was estimated as a successful choice for the construction of a greenhouse complex by foreign guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The most up-to-date technologies will be applied in the construction of greenhouses, a scientific center will be established within the complex. The Center will carry out works on personnel training and increasing the ability of use of new technologies for supporting producers working in the agrarian sector.</span></span></p>'),
