(5380, 'news', 288, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Admission of new members to the territorial organization of Garadagh region New Azerbaijan Party was conducted in the central office of &ldquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&rdquo; OJSC. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Attending the event, the Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Khalig Mammadov stated that the territorial organization had been founded some time before and the organizational works were carried out rapidly. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Later, cards were presented to the members of the party. The cards were presented by the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Abulfat Gojayev, deputy Aydın Huseynov, deputies chairman Khalig Mammadov and Elshan Asadov.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/28-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 949px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/28-1.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/28-4.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 662px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/28-5.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 909px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
