(5470, 'news', 294, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The President of Azerbaijan Republic İlham Aliyev participated at the opening ceremony of &ldquo;GRAND GAFGAZ&rdquo; trade complex. The Head of Ganja City Executive Power Elmar Valiyev gave information about the trade complex to the President.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The President Ilham Aliyev got acquainted with the fruit and vegetable sales area. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The head of our state was informed about the operations of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC represented in the complex. He was told that ecologically clean products procured at the average market price from all regions through vehicles are at first, directed to the demand of the state procurement organizations. The part of the products exceeding the demand is sent to the fairs organized at weekends in the capital and to the local markets. 40 thousand ton food products and agricultural products have been procured and directed to supply within the last 9 months of the current year and large amount of funds have been entered to the turnover of local producers. Planning improvement and expansion of the procurement and supply system, the Open Joint Stock Company plans to receive more products from the local manufacturers next year.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/23550401_2021227071494661_5254924476664379454_o.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/IMG_1105.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
