(5484, 'news', 295, 'en', 'title', 'THE DELEGATION VISITED CHINA PEOPLE’S REPUBLIC'),
(5485, 'news', 295, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The delegation of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC paid a business visit to China&rsquo;s People Republic. The delegation led by the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Abulfat Gojayev participated in XIV &ldquo;China new high technologies&rdquo; exhibition.&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The exhibition organized for the twenty fourth time has an international importance this year and scientific &ndash; technical achievements are exhibited here. The delegation of the Joint Stock Company got acquainted with the agricultural products and high technologies of the exhibition, intense elimination of poverty, activities of robot technology pavilion and conducted discussions in the direction of establishment of economic relations with the Chinese partners. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">An international conference was organized within the framework of the exhibition with the participation of the representatives of more than 50 countries including Azerbaijan, USA, New Zealand, England, Germany, Turkey, Russia, Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan. Making speech at the conference on behalf of the delegation, the Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Abulfat Gojayev gave detailed information about the economic reforms held in Azerbaijan. The speaker said that the economic potential of the country has been strengthened as a result of large-scale reforms realized under the leadership of the President of Azerbaijan Republic Ilham Aliyev, our country has become a favourable transport and logistics center. &ldquo;As it was in the history, Azerbaijan Republic takes an important place both from the geographical and commercial point of view in the realization of &ldquo;Great Silk Way&rdquo; project now too. Commissioning of Baku Tbilisi Gars railway project under the leadership of Azerbaijan will be useful for all countries, 17 million ton cargo and 2 million passengers will be transported through the railway and in its turn, it will strengthen incessant transport &ndash; logistics relations between Europe and Asia&rdquo; A.Gojayev said. The participants of the conference were informed about high potential in the agriculture of our country, investment attractiveness of the agrarian sector, as well as the operations of &laquo;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&raquo; OJSC.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The delegation of the Joint Stock Company visited one of the great business center of China People&rsquo;s Republic Shiyan city within the framework of the visit and was closely acquainted with the operations of the trade and sales centers. They also visited the business park &ldquo;Tan West Market&rdquo; considered as the starting point of Great Silk Way. Besides being a business center, &ldquo;Tan West Market&rdquo; is the center of culture and investment and takes a leading place among famous Chinese companies. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Then, a business meeting was conducted between the Chairman of the Board of Directors A.Gojayev and the governor of Shankhi province Khu Kheper. The development of future economic relations was discussed during the meeting and the Chinese delegation decided to visit Baku for the purpose of acquaintance. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The members of the delegation of the Joint Stock Company reviewed the modern gardens located in the Western part of China and agreed on the exchange of personnel within the framework of the visit and </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A reception was organized in honour of the delegation of Azerbaijan on the last day of the visit.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/23658635_2023636227920412_867648395375765963_n.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
