(5500, 'news', 296, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Khalig Mammadov opened the meeting and spoke about 10 &ndash; months activities of the company. He stated that setting as a target to be the cheapest supplier in the direction of nutritional and agricultural products in the country, Joint Stock Company has procured more than 53 thousand tons of product from the local producers and directed to supply for meeting the demand of the public procurement organizations within the current year. 43 thousand ton products have been exported to near and far foreign countries. The advance mechanism issued to the producers by the company has been carried out successfully, the financial support exerted positive impact on the development of economy. At present, the process of procurement of the products produced on the account of advance payments is being carried out. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Elshan Asadov, Deputy Director of the Department of procurement and work with the regional offices Vali Amirov, as well as, heads of the regional offices also made speeches and expressed their opinion about improvement of the procurement and supply system in the country. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\">Director of Strategic planning and Human resources department Muzaffer Ismayilov gave detailed information about the strategic development program being drawn up in the Joint Stock Company. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\">The forthcoming tasks were discussed at the end of the meeting.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/773462.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(5501, 'news', 296, 'en', 'short', 'Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Joint Stock Company Khalig Mammadov opened the meeting and spoke about 10 – months activities of the company. He stated that setting as a target to be the cheapest supplier in the direction of nutritional and agricultural products in the country, Joint Stock Company has procured more than 53 thousand tons of product from the local producers and directed to supply for meeting the demand of the public procurement organizations within the current year. 43 thousand ton products have been exported to near and far foreign countries. The advance mechanism issued to the producers by the company has been carried out successfully, the financial support exerted positive impact on the development of economy. At present, the process of procurement of the products produced on the account of advance payments is being carried out. '),
