(5530, 'news', 298, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Collaborators of Joint Stock Company &ndash; head of the Strategic development and human resources department Muzeffer Ismayilov, Head of human resources department Ramina Akbarova, Head of Public relations department Nijat Nasirli, Senior specialist Zibayat Ahmadova and leading specialists Zarif Asadova, Sabina Valiyeva attended &ldquo;HR SUMMİT BAKU-2017&rdquo;. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Such subjects as improvement of human resources management, adaptation of the employer brand to the requirements of modern era, role of IT technologies in the formation of staff were discussed in the forum attended by local and international experts.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/888.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 563px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
