(5649, 'news', 305, 'en', 'title', 'YOUTH DAY IN JOINT STOCK COMPANY'),
(5650, 'news', 305, 'en', 'full', '<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">An event was held at the &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply &quot; on the occasion of February 2 Youth Day. In the event, which was attended by young employees of Joint Stock Company, a video about the essence of the Youth Day was first considered. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors, Elshan Asadov congratulated the youth.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Nijat Nasirli, Public Affairs Officer spoke about the level of representation of youth in the procurement system. According to him, in accordance with the state policy, young people are widely represented in the Joint Stock Company. The majority of the staff are youth.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Zaur Bakhshaliyev, chairman of the NAP territorial organization, Youth Union, stressed that the approval of the State Program &quot;Azerbaijani Youth in 2017-2021&quot; signed by the President of the country will further enhance the role of youth in the development of society in the near future.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At the end of the event gifts were presented to young people.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0202.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0203.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0204.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0205.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0206.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0207.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0209.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/0208.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
