(5693, 'news', 307, 'en', 'keywords', 'the, and, iso, management, will, standards, working, system, company, standard, requirements, enhances, 9001, implementation, within, with, was, quality, opportunity, joint'),
(5694, 'news', 307, 'en', 'title', 'INTRODUCTION OF QUALITY CONTROL SYSTEM BASED ON ISO 9001:2015 STANDARDS'),
(5695, 'news', 307, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">For this purpose, the Chairman of the Board of Directors, Abulfat Gojayev, has signed a relevant decree on the establishment of a working group and conducting work on the establishment of the management system based on the ISO 9001: 2015 standard</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The working group will soon work on the implementation of the requirements of ISO 9001: 2015 at all stages of the supply and procurement system. In accordance with the action plan for the implementation of the management system within the execution period of February and July, the staff will be trained according to the ISO 9001: 2015 standard and necessary guidelines, procedures, various instructions will be prepared, risk analysis, risk map preparation and other important steps will be taken.&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Preparatory meeting with participation of working groups and related structural employees was held in Joint Stock Company. Deputy Chairman - Khalig Mammadov and Elshan Asadov talked about the advantages of the standards. It was noted that management standards are widely used worldwide today, and standards have been set up to facilitate international commodity and service exchange. The requirements of the standard cover all stages of the production-service chain and as a result, facilitates management, enhances control over product turnover, provides basis for the right division of responsibilities within the organization, serves to eliminate subjective factors, and enhances mutual trust among partners.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Coordinator of the Working Group, Head of &quot;Quality Management and Certification&quot; department, PhD in economics Galib Sharifov gave detailed information on the history, essence and application directions of ISO standards making presentation. It was emphasized that the application of ISO standards will increase the opportunity of attracting foreign investors to the Joint-Stock Company and the opportunity to participate in joint projects, and will bring preference in government programs, as well as in tenders. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/113-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 667px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/111-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 787px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/112.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>'),
(5696, 'news', 307, 'en', 'short', 'For this purpose, the Chairman of the Board of Directors, Abulfat Gojayev, has signed a relevant decree on the establishment of a working group and conducting work on the establishment of the management system based on the ISO 9001: 2015 standard'),
