(5859, 'news', 317, 'en', 'title', 'SOCIAL CAMPAIGN WAS HELD IN JOJUG MARJANLI'),
(5860, 'news', 317, 'en', 'full', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">A social campaign at the initiative of &quot;Food Products&rsquo; Procurement and Supply&quot; OJSC was held in Jojug Marjanli village of Jabrayil region, which was liberated from enemy occupation. Employees of the Joint Stock Company participated at the action organized on the occasion of Novruz holiday.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Firstly, in Horadiz, a monument to the memory of April martyrs was visited and wreaths and flowers were laid in front of it. The participants were informed about the course of the April wars, the great victory of the Azerbaijani Army, the strategic significance of the Lalatapa highland.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Later, the employees of the Joint Stock Company met with residents in the village of Jojug Marjanli. Deputy Head of the Jabrayil District Executive Authority Tapdig Nasirov spoke about the work carried out at the state level for the convenience of the population in the village.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Head of the Department Abbas Hajiyev and Head of the Department of Public Relations Nijat Nasirli, delivered Chief of Executive Board Abulfat Gojayev&rsquo;s, greetings to the residents. It was noted that the village was liberated as a result of the military campaign, which was carried out under the direct leadership of National Leader Heydar Aliyev, and renovated &nbsp;as a result of the will of the Supreme Commander-in-Chief Ilham Aliyev, as well as the people&#39;s prosperous &nbsp;life was provided. &quot;Jojug Marjanli&#39;s reconstruction is the result of the economic and military power of the Azerbaijani state. This village, which has become a symbol of freedom for our occupied lands, will be the beginning of the main road to Shusha, Khankandi in the near future&quot; the speakers emphasized.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">As part of the meeting with the population, 50 families settled in the village were given holiday gifts, and computer sets were delivered to the village secondary school.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Employees were closely acquainted with the reconstructed village after the occupation, and the Shusha Mosque was reviewed. The meeting with the Azerbaijani soldiers who served on the contact line created a good feeling among the employees.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Then there was a meeting with soldiers in the military unit N on the front line. Employees of the Joint Stock Company called on the soldiers to be brutal against the enemy. It was noted that the military-patriotic spirit of the soldiers serving the enemy on the contact line is at a high level.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">At the end of the event, the festive gifts were presented to the military unit on behalf of the Joint Stock Company and the meeting ended with a festive concert prepared by Fuzuli State Drama Theater.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/1.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/11.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 583px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/4048.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/666.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/3777.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/488.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload/Sedr/50000.JPG\" style=\"width: 750px; height: 500px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p>'),
(5861, 'news', 317, 'en', 'short', 'A social campaign at the initiative of \"Food Products’ Procurement and Supply\" OJSC was held in Jojug Marjanli village of Jabrayil region, which was liberated from enemy occupation. Employees of the Joint Stock Company participated at the action organized on the occasion of Novruz holiday.'),
